item.title: La Toile
item.description: Project members : AMADOR Clara LinkedIn LEGRY Louis LinkedIn FERAUD Alexandre LinkedIn FISCHER Julien LinkedIn BOBEUF Jules LinkedIn SANTORO Thomas LinkedIn I/ Explore “La Toile”, our virtual exposition created in 48 hours This is our latest university project: “La Toile “, a virtual exhibition of digital images. We chose to represent this exhibition in the form of the Paris metro, with each room representing a metro stop. Our goal was to create this site in only 48 hours and we are proud to have successfully overcome this challenge!
